    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Locks usually having a latch bolt controlled from both sides by knobs, with the latch arranged to be set by stops so that the outside knob is inoperative and entrance is gained by key only.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000038881/Stein, Construction Glossary (1980)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Cerraduras que generalmente poseen un cerrojo controlado por ambos lados por pomos, con el cerrojo arreglado para ser instalado por interrupciones para que el pomo exterior sea inoperante y la entrada sea alcanzada sólo con llave.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Spanish</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000131/CDBP-SNPC</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000051034/TAA database (2000-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Sloten die meestal over een vergrendelingsinrichting beschikken die van beide kanten met knoppen kan worden bediend. Hierbij is de klink zo afgesteld dat hij met pennen kan worden vastgezet, zodat de knop aan de buitenkant wordt geblokkeerd en men alleen met een sleutel naar binnen kan.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>一種以雙邊把手控制門閂的鎖，門閂可設定為禁止進入，此時外邊的把手便無法開啟門閂，一定要用鑰匙才能進入內部。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000250/AS-Academia Sinica</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
      </Descriptive_Note>
    </Descriptive_Notes>
